Package com.mjh.innaxyswebapp.model

Class Node

java.lang.Object
com.mjh.innaxyswebapp.model.Node
@Entity public class Node extends Object
Class which represents a node. The node itself contains its name, as well as its x and y-axis coordinates. Various getters and setters are available so as to provide specific information pertaining to the node.
Since:
02-10-2023
Version:
1.0
Author:
MaxMJH - MaxHarrisMJH@gmail.com
